doctype html
html
  head
    title= @title
    link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"
    css:
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 30px;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      }

      hgroup { margin-bottom: 30px; }
      h1 { margin: 0; }
      hgroup p { margin-top: 0; }

  body
    hgroup
      h1= @title
      p By <a href="http://henrik.nyh.se">Henrik Nyh</a>.

    p Enter 2â€“4 GitHub usernames to get a combined avatar for e.g. pair programming commits.

    - case @names.length
    - when 1
      p Moar!
    - when 2..4
      p: img src=@url
      p: input value=@url size=100

    form
      - 1.upto(4) do |i|
        p: label
          ' User #{i}:
          input name="name[]" value=@names[i-1]

      p: button Get avatar
